## 📝 What You’ll Learn in This Video

✅ **How carrier oils go rancid over time** and the risks involved  
✅ **How essential oils oxidise**, affecting aroma and skin safety  
✅ **Ways to test if an oil has gone off** at home  
✅ **When older oils may still be useful** for non-therapeutic uses  
✅ Tips for **reducing waste and maximising oil lifespan**

This guide helps you make smarter choices about when to keep or discard oils, keeping your blends fresh, effective, and safe.

